high_descs: Walk over to stand on the right side of the counter in front of you so you are facing it you should see two salt shakers on the far side..
Pick up the knife that's touching the spatula.
Walk to the opposite side of the island counter that's your on now looking towards the island.
Cut the potato to the right of the plate into slices.
Turn left and walk past the island then turn right and walk until the stove is on your left and when it is turn left and walk to it.
Put the knife in the pan on the bottom left burner.
Go back to the potato you cut up.
Pick up a slice of potato near the middle of the potato.
Walk back over to the stove.
Put the potato in the pan on the bottom left burner.
Pick up the pan with the potato and the knife.
Turn right and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the pan in the top portion towards the edge in the middle.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan that contains a slice of potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk towards the counter
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk with the knife towards the other side of the counter
Slice a potato on the counter
Walk with the knife towards the stove
Set the knife on the pan on the stove
Walk back to the counter where the slice potato is
Take a slice of the potato
Walk with the slice of the potato back to the stove
Put the slice of the potato on the pan
Grab the pan with the knife and potato
Walk with the pan towards the fridge
Open the fridge and set the pan inside
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, put the knife and slice of potato in pan, put pan in fridge

high_descs: Turn right, go towards the fridge, turn left, go to the short side of the island, face the island.
Take the knife from the island.
Go around the island to the opposite short side of the island.
Cut the potato next to the plate into slices.
Go around the island on its left and go to the oven to the left.
Put the knife in the pan on the front of the stove top.
Turn left, go back to the far short side of the island where the potato is.
Take a slice of potato.
Go around the island on its left and go to the oven to the left.
Put the potato in the pan on the front of the stove top.
Take the pan from the stove top.
Turn around, go to the fridge.
Put the pan on the the lowest shelf of the top compartment of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a slice of potato in a fridge.
